<br>
&quot;Oh Lord above the earth and sky, watching down upon on in your kingdom of angels and light.  I, Eli, your messanger and avatar, ask now for your blessing.. So that I may continue my way with a partner who has forever touched my heart.&quot;  <br>
<br>
There is a silence for a momment, and the clouds over head clear up... That was a yes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Alysia of the Amazons</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 4:17:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Blessings of the Amazon Ancients</span><hr size=1> Alysia then took the same position as Eli had done, placing his hand to her forehead as she called out to the Ancients.<br>
<br>
&quot;In the name of the reborn Atmah of which I have mothered to the Nation, I pray to the Amazon Ancients which we Scynthians respect and honor greatly. I Alysia, your Queen and Daughter ask in great respect the blessings such so that me and my partner may journey together through this life and onto eternity wherever our paths may meet. May we be there together.&quot;<br>
<br>
The wolf pack then gathered around the entire circle , their eyes glowing brightly. Each wolf then bowed down in that circle before Eli and Aly. . .that was the Ancients answer... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 5:30:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a blessing</span><hr size=1> Hera appeared before the couple in a blaze of dark blue light.  The cry of peacocks was heared echoing on the Scynthian Mountain sides.  She appeared in her usual black shimmering dressed, highlighted by small black peacock feathers.  Her icy blue eyes gazed down at the couple.  She knew they had their own gods.  But, Alysia did have respect for the Olympians.<br>
&quot;Hello Alysia,&quot;she spoke directly to Aly, then her icy blue eyes glanced at Eli warily. &quot;Hello Eli.  I don't know if you two had come to expect me to come.  But...I am the Goddess of Marriage. And,&quot;she smiles as sweetly as she can to Alysia. &quot;As I think dearly of Alysia, I thought I should come give this union my blessing.  Tho, I have seen many unions..and blessed many.. I can tell you both one important bit of wisdom.  It is not the blessings that you receive that shall keep this union unbroken.  It is your will and promise to make it work. In years to come....boredom and prettier mortals can come along. But, you shall have to make the decision to put all you can into this union.  That it shall remain unbroken and a proven love,&quot; her pale slim fingers dance upon each other's tips. Suddenly, before the couple appeared a small clay pot. &quot;I know this may seem a simple gift.  But, in it lies your hopes and dreams for a union that withstands time.  Right now, your union is the fresh newly made clay pot.  In time that pot shall change...to a wood, and then silver...then in time.. it shall be gold.  But... this change shall only occur as long as you both stay together and keep your promise of love, honour and truth.  The day that promise is broken.. it shall shatter and become ashes,&quot; she lifted a small white finger up, &quot;This symbolizes that it is up to the both of you to make your relationship golden and forever.  Don't worry...I still give you my blessings to your union.&quot; <br>
With that she suddenly dissappeared in a flash of light.  Leaving all to think of what she had said.  And the small clay pot sitting alone in front of them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=123.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=121.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm35">Amazon Nation Alliance<